审查以下贷款 disbursement 代码的风险。代码中直接调用了 loanRepo.save() 而没有创建 JournalEntry。

```java
public void disburse(Long loanId) {
    Loan loan = loanRepo.findById(loanId);
    loan.setStatus(LoanStatus.ACTIVE);
    loan.setDisbursedAmount(loan.getPrincipal());
    loanRepo.save(loan);
}
```

