以下代码中，`@Transactional` 的范围是否合适？

```java
@Transactional
public void processLoanRepayment(LoanRepaymentCommand cmd) {
    Loan loan = loanRepo.findById(cmd.getLoanId());
    loan.applyRepayment(cmd.getAmount());
    loanRepo.save(loan);
    notifyExternalSystem(cmd); // 外部 HTTP 调用
}
```
